OL,3,CLuther star Idris Elba to be knighted
OL,4,Cby King
OL,6,FActor Sir Idris Elba and ice skating
OL,7,Fchampions Dame Jayne Torvill and Sir
OL,8,FChristopher Dean will be among those
OL,9,Fto receive honours at Windsor Castle
OL,10,Fon Tuesday.
OL,12,FSome 68 people, including comedians
OL,13,FDame Meera Syal and Paul Elliott, one
OL,14,Fhalf of the double act Chuckle
OL,15,FBrothers, are due to be honoured by
OL,16,Fthe King.
OL,18,FLuther star Sir Idris was awarded a
OL,19,Fknighthood in the New Year Honours for
OL,20,Fservices to young people.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
