OL,3,CLuther star Idris Elba to be knighted
OL,4,Cby King
OL,6,FOlympic champions Dame Jayne and Sir
OL,7,FChristopher were also named in the New
OL,8,FYear Honours list, for services to ice
OL,9,Fskating and to voluntary service.
OL,11,FThe ice dancers, who later became the
OL,12,Ffaces of celebrity competition show
OL,13,FDancing On Ice, took home the Olympic
OL,14,Fgold at the 1984 Winter Games for
OL,15,Ftheir "Bolero" performance.
OL,17,FAfter finding out about the honour,
OL,18,FDame Jayne, 68, said the timing seemed
OL,19,F"perfect" after the two danced on the
OL,20,Fice for the final time last year.
