OL,3,CLuther star Idris Elba to be knighted
OL,4,Cby King
OL,6,FShe said: "We had such a great time,
OL,7,Fwe were so happy with the tour and the
OL,8,Ffact that we got through it.
OL,10,F"It was a big thing for us to mark our
OL,11,Fcareer before retirement, and then
OL,12,Freceiving this award at the end of the
OL,13,Fyear, it's just finished everything.
OL,14,FIt's perfect."
OL,16,FThe Kumars At No 42 star Dame Meera
OL,17,FSyal, 64, will be recognised by the
OL,18,FKing for services to literature, drama
OL,19,Fand charity.
