OL,3,CLuther star Idris Elba to be knighted
OL,4,Cby King
OL,6,FBorn in Wolverhampton, the actress had
OL,7,Fher breakthrough writing and starring
OL,8,Fin the BBC sketch show Goodness
OL,9,FGracious Me.
OL,11,FIn 2023 she was awarded the Bafta
OL,12,FFellowship, the academy's highest
OL,13,Faccolade for a career on screen.
OL,15,FRotherham comedian Paul Elliott, best
OL,16,Fknown as one of the Chuckle Brothers,
OL,17,Fwas made an Member of the Order of the
OL,18,FBritish Empire (MBE) for charitable
OL,19,Fservice.
