OL,3,CLuther star Idris Elba to be knighted
OL,4,Cby King
OL,6,FElliott has been a prominent supporter
OL,7,Fand ambassador for Marie Curie. The
OL,8,Fcharity's nurses provided end-of-life
OL,9,Fcare for Barry, and Paul previously
OL,10,Fspoke about how the nurses looked
OL,11,Fafter his brother "with incredible
OL,12,Fcare and kindness".
